01:23:45.796 --> 01:23:46.095
fruit.

01:23:47.957 --> 01:23:50.018
And he's empowered by the seven spirits of

01:23:50.057 --> 01:23:52.819
Yahowah to fulfill this role.

01:23:54.279 --> 01:23:55.900
But it's no easy job.

01:23:56.081 --> 01:23:58.462
The Israelites are a tough audience and

01:23:58.502 --> 01:24:00.042
the world is rife with rubbish.

01:24:01.069 --> 01:24:03.609
Those who engage with Yah are certain to

01:24:03.649 --> 01:24:06.671
be stained and stigmatized by the

01:24:06.711 --> 01:24:07.310
experience,

01:24:07.331 --> 01:24:08.771
and I can vouch for the fact that

01:24:08.811 --> 01:24:09.971
that is a reality,

01:24:10.372 --> 01:24:11.613
as it was for Yasha'yah.

01:24:13.132 --> 01:24:13.713
So clearly,

01:24:14.873 --> 01:24:18.055
the year of Yasha'yah's redemption has come.

01:24:18.074 --> 01:24:19.996
The prophet's revelations are now center

01:24:20.036 --> 01:24:20.456
stage,

01:24:21.377 --> 01:24:24.938
restoring Yisrael as the Ark of the

01:24:24.997 --> 01:24:27.139
Covenant is returned,

01:24:27.819 --> 01:24:30.539
carried into the place that it belonged

01:24:31.006 --> 01:24:32.167
back by the bull,

01:24:32.988 --> 01:24:35.992
just as he had hoped and foreseen.

01:24:36.953 --> 01:24:38.876
And while this was good news for the

01:24:38.895 --> 01:24:39.655
beneficiaries,

01:24:39.676 --> 01:24:42.560
the long line of naysayers who have

01:24:43.020 --> 01:24:45.662
precluded his message from resonating with

01:24:45.703 --> 01:24:46.144
his people,

01:24:47.055 --> 01:24:49.317
will suffer a day of recompense and

01:24:49.377 --> 01:24:50.096
retribution.

01:24:50.497 --> 01:24:53.279
The prophet will seek vengeance against

01:24:53.298 --> 01:24:55.920
the religious and political leaders that

01:24:55.960 --> 01:24:58.761
he has impugned in the opening ten

01:24:58.841 --> 01:25:01.643
chapters of Yasha'yah for the harm that they

01:25:01.682 --> 01:25:05.225
have done over the ages.

01:25:05.244 --> 01:25:08.246
Now this is important that we have made

01:25:08.305 --> 01:25:11.127
these connections because Yahowah intended

01:25:11.167 --> 01:25:11.328
them.

01:25:12.289 --> 01:25:14.850
and such that we are now the first

01:25:14.871 --> 01:25:18.412
to realize that Dowd's Obed-Edom is the

01:25:18.453 --> 01:25:21.573
same man who, three hundred years later,

01:25:21.654 --> 01:25:25.255
will be introduced by Yasha'yah Isaiah as

01:25:25.314 --> 01:25:28.076
the man who comes out of Edom to

01:25:28.155 --> 01:25:28.796
save many,

01:25:29.856 --> 01:25:32.457
and that he will be presented by Yahowah

01:25:32.597 --> 01:25:36.020
in the last days to accomplish this very

01:25:36.220 --> 01:25:36.420
goal.

01:25:38.239 --> 01:25:40.480
He will assume the responsibility,

01:25:40.980 --> 01:25:42.541
not only of returning the Ark of the

01:25:42.600 --> 01:25:44.962
Covenant so that Dowd can anoint it on

01:25:45.002 --> 01:25:47.603
Kipurym as is required in the Torah,

01:25:48.182 --> 01:25:51.144
but of so much more,

01:25:51.184 --> 01:25:54.645
preparing Yisrael for the Messiah's

01:25:54.685 --> 01:25:55.104
return.

01:25:59.086 --> 01:26:02.828
This will be the closing statement that

01:26:02.847 --> 01:26:06.069
I'll make today on Shamuel, listen to him,

01:26:06.168 --> 01:26:06.849
second Samuel.

01:26:08.390 --> 01:26:10.051
and we'll pick up the text at this

01:26:10.110 --> 01:26:12.252
place on Monday.

01:26:14.533 --> 01:26:17.055
Therefore, the Aaron,

01:26:19.435 --> 01:26:22.297
the ark as a means to behold the

01:26:22.318 --> 01:26:23.219
harvest of Yahowah,

01:26:25.619 --> 01:26:30.322
dwelt and remained in the Baath home of

01:26:30.443 --> 01:26:31.023
Obed-Edom,

01:26:32.042 --> 01:26:35.425
the one doing the work by serving from

01:26:35.865 --> 01:26:36.086
Edom.

01:26:37.153 --> 01:26:41.475
at the Gitti, the wine press.

01:26:41.494 --> 01:26:45.537
Three months while Yahowah blessed and

01:26:45.597 --> 01:26:48.139
commended, extolled the appropriateness,

01:26:48.179 --> 01:26:49.078
the usefulness,

01:26:51.520 --> 01:26:54.702
distinguishing an aspect of his nature to

01:26:54.922 --> 01:26:58.645
meet with and uplift Obed-Edom,

01:27:00.445 --> 01:27:02.226
the one doing the work while serving from

01:27:02.247 --> 01:27:02.506
Edom.

01:27:03.726 --> 01:27:06.569
In addition to all of his family,

01:27:07.462 --> 01:27:12.243
and every aspect of his home and his

01:27:12.283 --> 01:27:12.844
household.

01:27:14.444 --> 01:27:16.704
Extraordinary.

01:27:16.725 --> 01:27:18.905
Sham will listen to him, to Samuel six,

01:27:18.966 --> 01:27:19.305
eleven.

01:27:20.046 --> 01:27:21.166
So I'll leave you with those thoughts

01:27:21.225 --> 01:27:25.847
because it is evident that there's a very

01:27:25.908 --> 01:27:29.328
soft place in Yahowah's heart for

01:27:29.389 --> 01:27:29.868
Obed-Edom,

01:27:30.868 --> 01:27:34.489
just as there was in Yahshayah's for the

01:27:34.529 --> 01:27:35.130
man from Edom.

01:27:36.997 --> 01:27:38.840
And just as they are both connected with

01:27:38.899 --> 01:27:42.305
Dowd and the remnant of God's people and

01:27:42.324 --> 01:27:45.210
the proper positioning of the Ark of the

01:27:45.250 --> 01:27:45.631
Covenant.

01:27:46.953 --> 01:27:47.793
Thank you for listening.

01:27:48.215 --> 01:27:50.118
Have a wonderful rest of your Shabbat.

